  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/2bbbb06fc686e4462718c5f1b3bf0a99.poster.avif?t=1678038626\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/2bbbb06fc686e4462718c5f1b3bf0a99.webm?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/2bbbb06fc686e4462718c5f1b3bf0a99.mp4?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Rustled Pete</strong> is a boss fighting game. Do you have what it takes to show Pete who's the real boss?<br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You only have one life, but I'm sure you will manage!<br></li><li>Accumulate your combo counter and time your attacks to deal devastating blows to Pete!</li></ul><br><strong>I made some tools for you to stun Pete with, he doesn't like that at all!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/3fc44f4b5cd59ede63a3303de951040d.poster.avif?t=1678038626\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/3fc44f4b5cd59ede63a3303de951040d.webm?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/3fc44f4b5cd59ede63a3303de951040d.mp4?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Unlock new Pete Forms, and test your skills as he becomes angrier and angrier in each form!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/84f1f6589925688d349c595a6294b9c7.poster.avif?t=1678038626\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/84f1f6589925688d349c595a6294b9c7.webm?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/84f1f6589925688d349c595a6294b9c7.mp4?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>I could make you more tools to make your life a bit easier, but who are we kidding? You will die a lot any way!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/2bbbb06fc686e4462718c5f1b3bf0a99.poster.avif?t=1678038626\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/2bbbb06fc686e4462718c5f1b3bf0a99.webm?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/2bbbb06fc686e4462718c5f1b3bf0a99.mp4?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Rustled Pete</strong> is a boss fighting game. Do you have what it takes to show Pete who's the real boss?<br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You only have one life, but I'm sure you will manage!<br></li><li>Accumulate your combo counter and time your attacks to deal devastating blows to Pete!</li></ul><br><strong>I made some tools for you to stun Pete with, he doesn't like that at all!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/3fc44f4b5cd59ede63a3303de951040d.poster.avif?t=1678038626\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/3fc44f4b5cd59ede63a3303de951040d.webm?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/3fc44f4b5cd59ede63a3303de951040d.mp4?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Unlock new Pete Forms, and test your skills as he becomes angrier and angrier in each form!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/84f1f6589925688d349c595a6294b9c7.poster.avif?t=1678038626\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/84f1f6589925688d349c595a6294b9c7.webm?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081540/extras/84f1f6589925688d349c595a6294b9c7.mp4?t=1678038626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>I could make you more tools to make your life a bit easier, but who are we kidding? You will die a lot any way!",
